<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-01-10T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-01-10T18:00:00-05:00" n="134" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d134">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">125.7146/1–1050: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Consulate General at Peiping</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">secret   <gloss target="#t_niact1">niact</gloss>
                                </hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">us urgent</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-01-10T18:00:00-05:00">January
                                    10, 1950—6 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>25. Eyes only Clubb. <gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 22 Jan
                                10.<note n="1" xml:id="d134fn1">Not printed. It advised Mr. Clubb
                                that he should immediately smuggle out or secretly destroy the
                                post’s confidential files or reduce them to a minimum capable of
                                destruction at the last moment and should also remove the code
                                materials to a safe place. (125.7146/1–1050)</note> If ur Brit
                            colleague does not receive <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss>
                            instrs prior expiration time limit, you shld at last, resort arrange
                            direct or indirect means bring to attn Chou En-lai or other Commie
                            official views and intentions US Govt to ensure Commies not move against
                            US Govt property without full realization inevitable results such
                            action.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>